    return AuditedSettlementResult with
      buyerHolding = newBuyerHolding
      sellerHolding = newSellerHolding
      regulatorView = regulatorView  -- ✅ ALWAYS PRESENT
      settlementTime = now

KEY BENEFITS:
1. 100% Audit Coverage - No transactions can complete without audit
2. Atomic Guarantee - Settlement and audit succeed or fail together
3. Type Safety - Return type enforces audit creation
4. Compliance - Satisfies "Audit Everything, See Nothing Private"
5. Provable - Can verify completeness with AuditCompletenessCheck
-}
